node.text:
GLOBAL DAY OF COMPASSION‼️ 
SUNDAY - 7 • 25• 2021

Join @bigtkapone & me as we take a day to make the effort to show compassion to humanity.  There’s a few different initiatives to help on GDOC like Homelessness, Hunger etc. but 2moro we are aiming to help the Elderly in the Community. Let’s not forget about our Seniors who have raised us, taught us, & prayed for us!! 

IF YOU CARE ABOUT THE SENIORS IN OUR COMMUNITY & CAN, DONATE TO OUR CAUSE TO GET Food, Water, Gift Cards & more to the Seniors & Elders of our Community!! 
Thank You & God Bless 

LINK ⬇️ & IN MY BIO 

https://gofund.me/b57a6987

Salute the Empowering Our Youth For Tomorrow Foundation, Father’s Of The Community & A Fabolous Way
